console-settings.custom-start-script: import os import django from django.db.models import Q os.environ.setdefault("DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE", "todoproject.settings") django.setup() from django.db.models import * import sqlparse import pprint from todoapp.models import * def pq(qs): print sqlparse.format(str(qs.query), reindent=True) def pp(qs): pprint.pprint(list(qs))
